    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>Wines, not Wings</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/2722100376/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Wines, not Wings" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3103/2722100376_26d0b82923_m.jpg" height="180" width="240" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>I only caught this sign out of the corner of my drunken eye this evening.  At first, I was bemused that &quot;Rex-Goliath Wings&quot; would advertise with a rooster eating a drumstick. Only once I read it more clearly and realised what the rooster was *meant* to be holding did it seem lest tasteless (albeit mildly more bizarre)</p>
